\[\left(\sum_{i=1}^{m}\alpha_{i}x_{i}\right)^{\frac{1}{p}}\approx\left(\sum_{i= 1}^{m}\frac{1}{m}x_{i}\right)^{\frac{1}{p}}+\epsilon\cdot\frac{\sum e_{i}x_{i} ^{p}}{p\cdot\left(\sum\frac{1}{m}x_{i}^{p}\right)^{\frac{p-1}{p}}}\] (32)

